PRIVACY POLICY
Last revised: May 4, 2022
CODTEC SISTEMAS respects the privacy of users of its systems.
This Privacy Policy is intended to describe practices regarding the use of App Translation.
1- PERSONAL INFORMATION
No personal information is collected by CODTEC SISTEMAS.
All data is saved on the user's own device.
2- USE OF PERSONAL INFORMATION
CODTEC SISTEMAS does not use or share personal information.
If the user has further questions, he can send an e-mail to CODTEC SISTEMAS through the e-mail sac@codtec.com.
